{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"da951e12cf","title":"江青同志在“全国在京革命师生向资产阶级反动路线猛烈开火誓师大会”上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"16f2f33a75","index":0,"year":1966,"month":10,"day":6,"articleId":"da951e12cf"}],"tags":[{"id":"3457e40c94","name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"825563dd24","name":"清华大学毛泽东思想红卫兵《震五洲》战斗小组","type":"记录"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"097e8dc4-78a1-46bb-8b7e-467bb84632b7","name":"中央首长重要讲话（1967年）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"img","author":"毛泽东、江青、康生、张春桥、关锋，1967年左右","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/097e8dc4-78a1-46bb-8b7e-467bb84632b7/1.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/097e8dc4-78a1-46bb-8b7e-467bb84632b7/2.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/097e8dc4-78a1-46bb-8b7e-467bb84632b7/3.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/097e8dc4-78a1-46bb-8b7e-467bb84632b7/4.jpg"}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"097e8dc4-78a1-46bb-8b7e-467bb84632b7":{"comments":[{"id":"e27a16bba9","publicationId":"097e8dc4-78a1-46bb-8b7e-467bb84632b7","articleId":"da951e12cf","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"（转抄于清华大学毛泽东思想红卫兵《震五洲》战斗小组所整理）"}],"contents":[{"id":"d94ad7e5c3","type":"title","text":"江青同志十月六日下午在“全国在京革命师生向资产阶级反动路线猛烈开火誓师大会”上的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"097e8dc4-78a1-46bb-8b7e-467bb84632b7","articleId":"da951e12cf"},{"id":"ecb1c8c5f0","type":"appellation","text":"同志们，同学们：","index":1,"publicationId":"097e8dc4-78a1-46bb-8b7e-467bb84632b7","articleId":"da951e12cf"},{"id":"aacc053630","type":"paragraph","text":"你们好！我受党中央和毛主席的委托问你们好！中央文化革命小组全体同志向你们问好，向你们致崇高的无产阶级文化大革命的敬礼。","index":2,"publicationId":"097e8dc4-78a1-46bb-8b7e-467bb84632b7","articleId":"da951e12cf"},{"id":"682beba52e","type":"paragraph","text":"我们支持你们这种大无畏的无产阶级英雄行为，我们学习你们这种不怕困难，不怕牺牲的革命精神。我们坚决支持和你们站在一起，捍卫执行党中央关于无产阶级文化大革命的决定，即十六条。","index":3,"publicationId":"097e8dc4-78a1-46bb-8b7e-467bb84632b7","articleId":"da951e12cf"},{"id":"134bc296aa","type":"paragraph","text":"一个真正的无产阶级革命者一定要掌握原则，掌握政策，掌握策略。我希望同志们在斗争中掌握稳政策，善于斗争，在毛泽东思想的基础上，在斗争的考验中发展壮大左派队伍，团结大多数愿意革命的人，团结那些受蒙蔽的人，孤立和打击那一小撮党内走资本主义道路的当权派。","index":4,"publicationId":"097e8dc4-78a1-46bb-8b7e-467bb84632b7","articleId":"da951e12cf"},{"id":"fda110e84f","type":"paragraph","text":"党中央在十月五日批准了军队无产阶级文化大革命的紧急指示，现在请张春桥同志念一下，好不好？","index":5,"publicationId":"097e8dc4-78a1-46bb-8b7e-467bb84632b7","articleId":"da951e12cf"},{"id":"fc894c4343","type":"paragraph","text":"（群众：好）","index":6,"publicationId":"097e8dc4-78a1-46bb-8b7e-467bb84632b7","articleId":"da951e12cf"}],"page":{"id":"ec4ee7c7e1","publicationId":"097e8dc4-78a1-46bb-8b7e-467bb84632b7","articleId":"da951e12cf","start":3,"end":3}}}},"__N_SSG":true}